    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>A terminal user interface (TUI) factory flashing tool designed for high-concurrency ESP32 chip flashing on production lines.</description>
    <summary>PioPulse high-concurrency ESP32 factory flasher TUI.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/Wang-Yang-source/piopulse/releases</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright 2026 Wang Yang</copyright>
    <tags>esp32 flashing tui production-line development</tags>
